    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts precisely, offering a very dependable and comfortable driving experience. While the exterior shows some minor signs of regular use, such as a few small stone chips and light surface scratches, the paint still retains a healthy shine. The interior is clean and well-preserved, with all electronics, gauges, and climate controls functioning exactly as they should. It is a solid, reliable choice for anyone looking for a well-cared-for pre-owned car.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
